@* قائمة الخصم اليدوي للبيع — بنفس نظام قائمة الأصناف (شريط فلاتر، جدول، ترقيم، تاب لتقرير الأرصدة) *@
@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Html
@using ERP.Infrastructure
@model PagedResult<ERP.ViewModels.ProductDiscountEffectiveRow>

@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "قائمة الخصم اليدوي للبيع";
    var action = Convert.ToString(ViewContext.RouteData.Values["action"]) ?? "Index";
    var controller = Convert.ToString(ViewContext.RouteData.Values["controller"]) ?? "ProductDiscountOverrides";

    var search = Model.Search ?? (string?)ViewBag.Search ?? "";
    var searchBy = (string?)ViewBag.SearchBy ?? "product";
    var sort = (Model.SortColumn ?? (string?)ViewBag.Sort ?? "product").Trim().ToLowerInvariant();
    var dir = Model.SortDescending ? "desc" : ((string?)ViewBag.Dir ?? "asc");
    dir = string.Equals(dir, "desc", StringComparison.OrdinalIgnoreCase) ? "desc" : "asc";

    int ps = Model.PageSize;
    int total = Model.TotalCount;
    int page = Model.PageNumber;
    int pages = Model.TotalPages;
    int start = total == 0 ? 0 : ((page - 1) * ps) + 1;
    int end = Math.Min(total, page * ps);
    int first = 1, last = Math.Max(1, pages);
    int prev = Math.Max(first, page - 1);
    int next = Math.Min(last, page + 1);

    bool useDateRange = Model.UseDateRange;
    DateTime? fromDate = Model.FromDate;
    DateTime? toDate = Model.ToDate;

    string Link(int p) => Url.Action(action, controller, new { search, searchBy, sort, dir, page = p, pageSize = ps, useDateRange, fromDate, toDate })!;

    Func<string, string, IHtmlContent> sortLink = (col, caption) =>
    {
        var colLower = (col ?? "").Trim().ToLowerInvariant();
        var isCurrent = string.Equals(sort, colLower, StringComparison.OrdinalIgnoreCase);
        var newDir = (isCurrent && dir == "asc") ? "desc" : "asc";
        var url = Url.Action(action, controller, new { search, searchBy, sort = colLower, dir = newDir, page = 1, pageSize = ps, useDateRange, fromDate, toDate }) ?? "#";
        string icon = isCurrent ? (dir == "asc" ? "▲" : "▼") : "⇅";
        return new HtmlString($@"<a href=""{url}"" class=""text-decoration-none text-dark"">{caption} <span class=""erp-sort-icon"">{icon}</span></a>");
    };
}

<div dir="rtl" class="container-fluid">
    @* ===== شريط الفلاتر الموحد (نفس نظام قائمة الأصناف) ===== *@
    <div class="erp-list-filter-bar d-print-none mt-2">
        <div class="row g-3 align-items-center flex-wrap justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-12 col-lg-5 erp-filter-section d-flex flex-column align-items-center">
                <form method="get" action="@Url.Action(action, controller)" class="erp-list-search-form d-flex flex-column align-items-center w-100">
                    <label class="form-label w-100 text-center">بحث في الخصم اليدوي</label>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-wrap align-items-center gap-2 erp-list-search-row justify-content-center w-100">
                        <input type="text" name="search" class="form-control erp-filter-input" placeholder="نص البحث..." value="@search" />
                        <select name="searchBy" class="form-select form-select-arrow erp-filter-input" style="max-width:160px">
                            @foreach (var opt in (IEnumerable<Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc.Rendering.SelectListItem>)ViewBag.SearchOptions)
                            {
                                <option value="@opt.Value" @(opt.Selected ? "selected" : null)>@opt.Text</option>
                            }
                        </select>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-erp btn-erp-primary btn-erp-sm">بحث</button>
                        <a class="btn btn-erp btn-erp-secondary btn-erp-sm text-decoration-none" href="@Url.Action(action, controller)">إلغاء</a>
                    </div>
                    <input type="hidden" name="sort" value="@sort" />
                    <input type="hidden" name="dir" value="@dir" />
                    <input type="hidden" name="page" value="1" />
                    <input type="hidden" name="pageSize" value="@ps" />
                    <input type="hidden" name="useDateRange" value="@(useDateRange ? "true" : "false")" />
                    @if (fromDate.HasValue) { <input type="hidden" name="fromDate" value="@fromDate.Value.ToString("o")" /> }
                    @if (toDate.HasValue) { <input type="hidden" name="toDate" value="@toDate.Value.ToString("o")" /> }
                </form>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 col-lg-5 erp-filter-section d-flex flex-column align-items-center">
                <label class="form-label d-none d-md-block" style="visibility:hidden">أوامر</label>
                <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 justify-content-center">
                    <a class="btn btn-erp btn-erp-primary btn-erp-sm erp-open-in-tab" href="@Url.Action("ProductBalances", "Reports", new { loadReport = true })" data-tab-id="product-balances-report" data-tab-title="تقرير: أرصدة الأصناف" title="يفتح في تاب جديد أو في تاب التقرير إن كان مفتوحاً">
                        📊 تقرير أرصدة الأصناف
                    </a>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-erp btn-erp-secondary btn-erp-sm" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#dateFilterModal">فلترة بالتاريخ</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    @* ===== عنوان الجدول وإجمالي السجلات ===== *@
    <div class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-between align-items-center mt-3 mb-2">
        <h5 class="mb-0">@ViewData["Title"]</h5>
        @if (total > 0)
        {
            <small class="text-muted">إجمالي السجلات: <span id="productDiscountOverridesCount">@total</span></small>
        }
    </div>
    <p class="text-muted small mb-2">يظهر هنا <strong>كل صنف له رصيد</strong> (في أي مخزن). العمود «الخصم %» = الخصم الفعّال (يدوي إن وُجد، وإلا الخصم المرجّح). مصدر الخصم: يدوي = من جدول الخصم اليدوي، مرجّح = محسوب من المشتريات.</p>

    @* ===== جدول البيانات (نفس تنسيق قائمة الأصناف) ===== *@
    <div class="erp-table-scroll-container mt-3">
        <div class="erp-table-wrapper erp-print-area" style="position: relative; max-height: 70vh; overflow-y: auto; overflow-x: auto;">
            <table class="table table-striped table-hover mb-0 erp-table erp-table-sortable">
                <thead class="table-light" style="position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 10; background: #fafbfc !important;">
                    <tr>
                        <th data-col="id">@sortLink("id", "رقم #")</th>
                        <th data-col="product">@sortLink("product", "المنتج")</th>
                        <th data-col="warehouse">@sortLink("warehouse", "المخزن")</th>
                        <th data-col="batch">التشغيلة</th>
                        <th class="text-end" data-col="discount">@sortLink("discount", "الخصم %")</th>
                        <th data-col="source">مصدر الخصم</th>
                        <th data-col="reason">السبب</th>
                        <th data-col="createdby">أنشأه</th>
                        <th data-col="created">@sortLink("created", "تاريخ الإنشاء")</th>
                        <th class="no-print" data-col="actions">أوامر</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    @if (!Model.Items.Any())
                    {
                        <tr><td colspan="10" class="text-center text-muted py-4">لا توجد بيانات.</td></tr>
                    }
                    else
                    {
                        foreach (var x in Model.Items)
                        {
                            var isManual = x.IsManual && x.OverrideId.HasValue;
                            <tr>
                                <td>@(isManual ? x.OverrideId!.ToString() : "—")</td>
                                <td>@(x.ProductName) (@(x.ProdCode))</td>
                                <td>@x.WarehouseName</td>
                                <td>الكل</td>
                                <td class="text-end">
                                    @if (isManual)
                                    {
                                        <input form="formUpdate_@(x.OverrideId)" type="number" name="overrideDiscountPct" step="0.01" min="0" max="100" value="@x.EffectiveDiscountPct.ToString("N2", System.Globalization.CultureInfo.InvariantCulture)" class="form-control form-control-sm text-end" style="width:70px; margin-left:auto;" />
                                    }
                                    else
                                    {
                                        @x.EffectiveDiscountPct.ToString("N2")
                                    }
                                </td>
                                <td>@(x.IsManual ? "يدوي" : "مرجّح")</td>
                                <td>
                                    @if (isManual)
                                    {
                                        <input form="formUpdate_@(x.OverrideId)" type="text" name="reason" value="@(x.Reason ?? "")" class="form-control form-control-sm" maxlength="200" style="max-width:140px;" />
                                    }
                                    else
                                    {
                                        @(x.Reason ?? "—")
                                    }
                                </td>
                                <td>@(x.CreatedBy ?? "—")</td>
                                <td>@(x.CreatedAt.HasValue ? x.CreatedAt.Value.ToString("yyyy/MM/dd HH:mm") : "—")</td>
                                <td class="no-print">
                                    @if (isManual)
                                    {
                                        <form id="formUpdate_@(x.OverrideId)" method="post" asp-action="Update" asp-route-id="@(x.OverrideId)" class="d-inline">
                                            @Html.AntiForgeryToken()
                                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-erp btn-erp-primary btn-erp-sm">حفظ</button>
                                        </form>
                                        <a asp-action="Edit" asp-route-id="@(x.OverrideId)" class="btn btn-erp btn-erp-secondary btn-erp-sm">تعديل</a>
                                        <form method="post" asp-action="Delete" asp-route-id="@(x.OverrideId)" class="d-inline" onsubmit="return confirm('حذف سجل الخصم اليدوي لهذا الصنف؟');">
                                            @Html.AntiForgeryToken()
                                            <input type="hidden" name="id" value="@(x.OverrideId)" />
                                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-erp btn-erp-danger btn-erp-sm">مسح</button>
                                        </form>
                                    }
                                    else
                                    {
                                        <span class="text-muted">—</span>
                                    }
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        }
                    }
                </tbody>
                @if (Model.Items.Any())
                {
                    <tfoot class="table-secondary fw-bold">
                        <tr>
                            <td colspan="9" class="text-end">عدد السجلات (حسب الفلتر):</td>
                            <td class="text-end">@total</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tfoot>
                }
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>

    @* ===== الترقيم (نفس شكل قائمة الأصناف) ===== *@
    @if (total > 0)
    {
        <div class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-between align-items-center gap-3 mt-2 no-print">
            <small class="text-muted">عرض @start - @end من @total</small>
            <nav aria-label="ترقيم">
                <ul class="pagination pagination-sm mb-0">
                    <li class="page-item @(page <= 1 ? "disabled" : "")">
                        <a class="page-link" href="@Link(1)">الأول</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="page-item @(page <= 1 ? "disabled" : "")">
                        <a class="page-link" href="@Link(prev)">السابق</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="page-item disabled"><span class="page-link">@(page) / @(last)</span></li>
                    <li class="page-item @(page >= last ? "disabled" : "")">
                        <a class="page-link" href="@Link(next)">التالي</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="page-item @(page >= last ? "disabled" : "")">
                        <a class="page-link" href="@Link(last)">الأخير</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
            <form method="get" action="@Url.Action(action, controller)" class="d-inline">
                <input type="hidden" name="search" value="@search" />
                <input type="hidden" name="searchBy" value="@searchBy" />
                <input type="hidden" name="sort" value="@sort" />
                <input type="hidden" name="dir" value="@dir" />
                <input type="hidden" name="page" value="1" />
                <input type="hidden" name="useDateRange" value="@(useDateRange ? "true" : "false")" />
                @if (fromDate.HasValue) { <input type="hidden" name="fromDate" value="@fromDate.Value.ToString("o")" /> }
                @if (toDate.HasValue) { <input type="hidden" name="toDate" value="@toDate.Value.ToString("o")" /> }
                <label class="me-1">حجم الصفحة:</label>
                <select name="pageSize" class="form-select form-select-sm d-inline-block" style="width:auto" onchange="this.form.submit()">
                    <option value="25" selected="@(ps == 25)">25</option>
                    <option value="50" selected="@(ps == 50)">50</option>
                    <option value="100" selected="@(ps == 100)">100</option>
                    <option value="200" selected="@(ps == 200)">200</option>
                </select>
            </form>
        </div>
    }

    @* مودال فلترة بالتاريخ (نفس نمط قائمة الأصناف) *@
    <div class="modal fade" id="dateFilterModal" tabindex="-1">
        <div class="modal-dialog">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <form method="get" action="@Url.Action(action, controller)">
                    <div class="modal-header">
                        <h5 class="modal-title">فلترة بالتاريخ (تاريخ الإنشاء)</h5>
                        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-body">
                        <div class="form-check mb-2">
                            <input type="checkbox" name="useDateRange" value="true" id="useDateRange" class="form-check-input" @(useDateRange ? "checked" : "") />
                            <label for="useDateRange" class="form-check-label">تفعيل فلترة التاريخ</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-2">
                            <label class="form-label">من</label>
                            <input type="datetime-local" name="fromDate" class="form-control" value="@(fromDate?.ToString("yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mm") ?? "")" />
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label class="form-label">إلى</label>
                            <input type="datetime-local" name="toDate" class="form-control" value="@(toDate?.ToString("yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mm") ?? "")" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-footer">
                        <input type="hidden" name="search" value="@search" />
                        <input type="hidden" name="searchBy" value="@searchBy" />
                        <input type="hidden" name="sort" value="@sort" />
                        <input type="hidden" name="dir" value="@dir" />
                        <input type="hidden" name="page" value="1" />
                        <input type="hidden" name="pageSize" value="@ps" />
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-erp btn-erp-primary">تطبيق</button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">إغلاق</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    @* فتح تقرير أرصدة الأصناف في تاب (نفس التاب إن كان مفتوحاً أو تاب جديد) *@
    <script>
        (function () {
            document.querySelectorAll('a.erp-open-in-tab').forEach(function (a) {
                a.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                    e.preventDefault();
                    var url = (a.getAttribute('href') || '').trim();
                    if (!url) return;
                    url = url + (url.indexOf('?') >= 0 ? '&' : '?') + 'frame=1';
                    var tabId = (a.getAttribute('data-tab-id') || 'product-balances-report').trim();
                    var title = (a.getAttribute('data-tab-title') || 'تقرير: أرصدة الأصناف').trim();
                    if (window.top !== window && window.top.erpTabs && typeof window.top.erpTabs.openTab === 'function') {
                        window.top.erpTabs.openTab(tabId, url, title);
                    } else {
                        window.location.href = url;
                    }
                });
            });
        })();
    </script>
</div>
